    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Medals, usually Dutch but also found in South Africa and elsewhere, issued to raise money for the victims of wars or natural disasters, for arts patronage, nature preservation, or another cause. They are considered numismatic collectibles.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
